-208-08-1536x1024.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe loft’s upper level houses luxurious bedroom suites, complete with spa-like bathrooms, as seen in this bedroom that includes a glass-enclosed en-suite.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1277\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bedroom-glass-enclosed-ensuite-bathroom-250325-207-09.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom that includes a glass-enclosed en-suite bathroom.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bedroom-glass-enclosed-ensuite-bathroom-250325-207-09.jpg 1277w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bedroom-glass-enclosed-ensuite-bathroom-250325-207-09-940x1884.jpg 940w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bedroom-glass-enclosed-ensuite-bathroom-250325-207-09-800x1604.jpg 800w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bedroom-glass-enclosed-ensuite-bathroom-250325-207-09-768x1540.jpg 768w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bedroom-glass-enclosed-ensuite-bathroom-250325-207-09-766x1536.jpg 766w, https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bedroom-glass-enclosed-ensuite-bathroom-250325-207-09-1022x2048.jpg 1022w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1277px) 100vw, 1277px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eIn another bathroom, an artistic floral mural features on the wall, adding color to the room.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1920\" height=\"2560\" src=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bathroom-floral-mural-250325-206-10.jpg\" alt=\"An artistic floral mural features on the wall of this bathroom, adding color to the room.\" srcset=\"https://www.contemporist.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/modern-bath